<h3 id="1-the-motivation">1 The motivation</h3>

<p>In the first few days, the motivation was huge.</p>

<p>When I had the idea of helping PD patients on recieving better and more accurate medication, I was determined to do my best and become the change to launch this wearable tech device. My eye was on the final outcome â€“ Nung, this is why the ball is parallel to the end goal.</p>

<p>I can see and vision the goal, but to achieve it thereâ€™s a long way ahead.</p>

<h3 id="2-the-dip">2 The dip</h3>

<p>As I started to delve into all sorts of research research and research, I slowly realized there werenâ€™t any pre-existing product on this PD idea. Many ideas were on how to find or discover people with Parkinsonâ€™s Diease earlier. However, not much were being done in the process of having PD.
